Problem → Students hesitate to ask doubts due to fear/shame.

Solution → Anonymous Q&A platform for students, live feed for professors.

Scope for Phase 1 →
✅ Student submits anonymous question
✅ Professor sees all questions in dashboard
✅ Mark questions as answered
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
MVP Features (Minimum Working App):

Student Side: Submit anonymous question

Professor Side: Login → View questions → Mark answered

Future Features (After MVP works):

Upvote questions

Categorize by subject/topic

Live updates (Socket.IO)

Analytics (most asked topic, common doubts)